sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager
actor QM as QA Manager
actor DQM as DEQA Manager
actor LEAD as DEQA Lead

participant UI as QA Dashboard UI
participant BFF as Quality Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant QA as Quality Management Service
participant DEQA as DEQA Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open QA dashboard
UI->>BFF: Load role-based QA worklist
BFF->>ORCH: Get worklist by role
ORCH->>QA: Fetch internal QA records by role/status
QA->>READDB: Read project_qa_wbs
READDB-->>QA: Internal QA rows
ORCH->>DEQA: Fetch DEQA records by role/status
DEQA->>READDB: Read deqa_request
READDB-->>DEQA: DEQA rows
DEQA-->>ORCH: DEQA worklist response
QA-->>ORCH: QA worklist response
ORCH-->>BFF: Aggregated role-specific response
BFF-->>UI: Show role-relevant records and CTAs
